title: Mobile Suit Gundam 00I 2314
sinopse:
Mobile Suit Gundam 00I 2314 occurs within the timeline of Mobile Suit Gundam 00 The Movie: A wakening of the Trailblazer.
The manga features the revived Celestial Being shadow group known as Fereshte, and their encounters with the ELS.

(Source: Gundam Wikia).
